Reconstructive aortic valve surgery in the elderly: Techniques and outcomes.

Urbanski PP(1), Jankulovski A(2), Doldurov K(2), Zhan X(2), Sodah A(2), Zacher 
M(2), Diegeler A(2).

Author information:
(1)Cardiovascular Clinic Bad Neustadt, Bad Neustadt, Germany. Electronic 
address: p.urbanski@herzchirurgie.de.
