The slowing pace of life expectancy gains since 1950.

Cardona C(1), Bishai D(2).

Author information:
(1)Department of Population, Family and Reproductive Health, Johns Hopkins 
Bloomberg School of Public Health, 615 N. Wolfe Street, Baltimore, MD, 21205, 
