Trends in the performance of quality indicators for diabetes care in the 
community and in diabetes-related health status: an Israeli ecological study.

Calderon-Margalit R(1), Cohen-Dadi M(2), Opas D(2), Jaffe DH(2), Levine J(2), 
Ben-Yehuda A(3), Paltiel O(2), Manor O(2).

Author information:
(1)Hadassah-Hebrew University Braun School of Public Health, POB 12272, 9112102, 
